reviews.review_text: Second Set!!! This show is a really great sound quality, with a really good first set a good amount of up-tempo songs, and Brent really came to play tonight (as if he ever didn't) Just a little Light in the first and then I will take you home is the one that hits home in the second set, but the entire second set is non-stop from start to finish opening with a fantastic scarlet fire than a wild 17 min truckin' just and all around climatic end to a three night run, God I miss Brent!
